block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"71b5d676-895e-4ab7-99f2-5ccf68b847ca":{"value":{"id":"71b5d676-895e-4ab7-99f2-5ccf68b847ca","version":1396,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["因为自媒体的繁荣，很大程度上对传统媒体产生了巨大的冲击。传统官媒有了极大的压力，他们不得不也加入到大众媒体的行列中，无论什么新闻也要凑个热闹，所以常常看到第一资源的自媒体用户发布后，他们会立即跟进，二次助力，甚至不会去验明事件的真实性，只做了一遍“转发”。"]]},"created_time":1714028341192,"last_edited_time":1714030767914,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"b5c1d092-28af-488f-82e9-b2a0b1ec628b":{"value":{"id":"b5c1d092-28af-488f-82e9-b2a0b1ec628b","version":413,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["新闻好像越来越不严肃了，以前的新闻还会被划分板块：时事、娱乐、军事… 现在好像都变成了娱乐新闻。"]]},"created_time":1714028701901,"last_edited_time":1714028749450,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"a81c3437-1cb6-4829-bbb1-1f329cc181a7":{"value":{"id":"a81c3437-1cb6-4829-bbb1-1f329cc181a7","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1714028750410,"last_edited_time":1714028750410,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"2b7242b3-4bab-4c96-a651-39419766976f":{"value":{"id":"2b7242b3-4bab-4c96-a651-39419766976f","version":184,"type":"sub_header","properties":{"title":[["附：关于“发现石油”会不会触发定位的“专业”理解",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1714028750209,"last_edited_time":1714031147776,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"9a349be6-3668-4d7a-95f9-84161831845d":{"value":{"id":"9a349be6-3668-4d7a-95f9-84161831845d","version":364,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["作为一名从事软件行业的人分析这件事，是不太可能的。"]]},"created_time":1714028132151,"last_edited_time":1714030790026,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"9906d23b-828e-430d-9eec-0d7bc9a42ff3":{"value":{"id":"9906d23b-828e-430d-9eec-0d7bc9a42ff3","version":105,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["安全的本质是“收益与成本”",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1714028974440,"last_edited_time":1714031141069,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"44ffead0-14a1-4779-a22a-b3d916131b18":{"value":{"id":"44ffead0-14a1-4779-a22a-b3d916131b18","version":654,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["首先，没有绝对安全的软件、硬件。任何系统皆如此。"]]},"created_time":1714028887049,"last_edited_time":1714029507776,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"882b234f-39d1-425c-9d1d-e83aa9f10682":{"value":{"id":"882b234f-39d1-425c-9d1d-e83aa9f10682","version":1797,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["可靠的本质是“成本收益与比足够高”。这件事如果为真，苹果方收益是什么呢？但他付出的成本又会是什么呢？作为全球市值最高的科技公司，一旦被发现，产生的全球信任危机，会让他付出极大的成本，甚至一蹶不振。而收益呢？所以从受益于成本来看，苹果不太可能会可以去做这件事。"]]},"created_time":1714028996370,"last_edited_time":1714030815133,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"92335a94-5caa-4e4a-9b33-c21a0663e1e1":{"value":{"id":"92335a94-5caa-4e4a-9b33-c21a0663e1e1","version":1835,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["同理，常常会看到“xx 软件监听用户日常讲话”。其实也只需要思考一下，如果为真，这件事的收益与成本分别是什么。单是对用户日常语音分析就是一个非常大的难题，全天候监听并分析，只为了提取出几个商品关键词？这件事想想也不划算。相比之下，通过分析用户的搜索、浏览、交互行为是更高效的方法。"]]},"created_time":1714029637763,"last_edited_time":1714030879961,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"e4ff544a-6dda-4e98-aa9e-aadbb0dc92a6":{"value":{"id":"e4ff544a-6dda-4e98-aa9e-aadbb0dc92a6","version":610,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["这也是选择“大品牌”的一个优点，做同一件事，大品牌会考虑更多，不会想着只做一锤子买卖。所以买大品牌也并非是智商税。"]]},"created_time":1714030900692,"last_edited_time":1714030994468,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"dff527e2-4307-49dc-9f35-bd0f98d64867":{"value":{"id":"dff527e2-4307-49dc-9f35-bd0f98d64867","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1714029091691,"last_edited_time":1714029091691,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"a9ceef1c-ec68-431e-82c2-f778a60759dc":{"value":{"id":"a9ceef1c-ec68-431e-82c2-f778a60759dc","version":109,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["公开透明才更安全",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1714029091561,"last_edited_time":1714031151348,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"a50fb8c1-7957-406b-99a8-2cf23d1193d1":{"value":{"id":"a50fb8c1-7957-406b-99a8-2cf23d1193d1","version":1207,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["公开透明才能让用户更有信心。相比之下，苹果在数据安全保护上做的还是不错的。至少软件在调用摄像头、位置信息、麦克风等设备时，都会出现明显的提示图标。因为这个，也才会有这则新闻出现。"]]},"created_time":1714029577777,"last_edited_time":1714031026672,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"360875e8-8101-4f25-975f-84bcc6becc11":{"value":{"id":"360875e8-8101-4f25-975f-84bcc6becc11","version":1699,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["想想这则新闻，很难不让人觉得这不是炒作。在一个地图软件上，搜索任意字符都会出现位置图标的。以此类推，发送任意一段语音，同样也会出现麦克风的图标。所以制造这则新闻的人，并不算太高明。应该提供更加有说服力的证据，如网络抓包数据等，"],["至少证明这条位置信息确实是发送给了苹果方，而不是软件服务方",[["b"]]],["。"]]},"created_time":1714030200315,"last_edited_time":1714031090101,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"eda619cf-32eb-4ae0-a414-859d4321687f":{"value":{"id":"eda619cf-32eb-4ae0-a414-859d4321687f","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1714030422960,"last_edited_time":1714030422960,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"2d953f4a-14f0-4991-8319-e2b7cf24a1c0":{"value":{"id":"2d953f4a-14f0-4991-8319-e2b7cf24a1c0","version":128,"type":"sub_sub_header","properties":{"title":[["个人信息安全注意事项",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1714030422165,"last_edited_time":1714031154336,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"3fb75611-a13e-49ae-b22d-08596b33d677":{"value":{"id":"3fb75611-a13e-49ae-b22d-08596b33d677","version":621,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["虽然特定攻击具体某个人的成本收益比非常高，但是我们很可能成为批量攻击的目标范围之一，所以仍然还是需要注意个人信息安全保护。"]]},"created_time":1714030451393,"last_edited_time":1714030574890,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"a6322ddd-c05a-48fc-b681-adc7379d796b":{"value":{"id":"a6322ddd-c05a-48fc-b681-adc7379d796b","version":3,"type":"alias","format":{"alias_pointer":{"id":"dea4f9dd-2de0-4ae3-bf41-e7b01cbbf39a","table":"block","spaceId":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"}},"created_time":1714030623487,"last_edited_time":1714030623487,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"165df8aa-4269-4129-b08b-430abd0481bf":{"value":{"id":"165df8aa-4269-4129-b08b-430abd0481bf","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1714031092727,"last_edited_time":1714031092727,"parent_id":"d8460d8f-a231-4b64-9003-5923c201af40","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c907765